<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="<txp:lang />" dir="<txp:text item="lang_dir" />">

<txp:output_form form="head" bodyclass="" />

<txp::u_debug title='page: <txp:page_url type="page" />' />

<txp::o_header_common />

<main class="b_typeset l_width-limited l_width-limited--large u_p" aria-label="<txp:text item="main_content" />" itemscope <txp::a_itemtype />>
  <txp:section title wraptag="h1" />

    <details>
    <summary><h2>Form: Shifty</h2></summary>
    <p>For Shifty to display, specify article images on an article using forms/article/shifty.txp</p>
    <txp:article limit="1" sort="rand()" form="shifty" article_image />
  </details>
  <hr />
  <details>
    <summary><h2>Form: Super pan</h2></summary>
    <p>For Super pan to display, specify article images on an article using forms/article/super_pan.txp</p>
    <txp:article limit="1" sort="rand()" form="super_pan" />
  </details>
    <hr />
  <details>
    <summary><h2>Form: Carousel</h2></summary>
    <p>Use Carousel by specifying its shortcode:</p>
    <code>&lt;txp::o_carousel id=&apos;&lt;txp:variable name=&quot;images&quot; /&gt;&apos; class=&quot;a_ratio--gm&quot; /&gt;</code>

  <txp:variable name="images" trim>
    <txp:images sort="category desc, rand()" limit="10" break=","><txp:image_info type="id" /></txp:images>
  </txp:variable>
    <txp::o_carousel id='<txp:variable name="images" />' class="a_ratio--gm u_m--tt" classfigure=""/>
  </details>
  <hr />

  <details>
  <summary><h2>All together now</h2></summary>
    <p><a href="/together/">View the site using multiple viewports</a> for quick responsive testing.</p>
    <p>Create a section with name <em>together</em> and assign /pages/together.txp to it.</p>
  </details>

</main>

<txp::o_footer/>
<txp::o_javascript />

</body>

</html>